query:
DELETE c1 FROM clientes c1
INNER JOIN clientes c2 ON c1.clienteHash = c2.clienteHash
WHERE c1.id < c2.id 
   OR (c1.id != c2.id AND c1.qualidadeScore < c2.qualidadeScore);
